snippet.title: Mon Aamar Ek Natun | Bengali Movie Video Song | Biyer Phool | Prosenjit Chatterjee, Rani Mukerji

localized.description:
Presenting you the song "Mon Aamar Ek Natun" from the movie Biyer Phool(1996) directed by Ram Mukherjee, starring Prosenjit Chatterjee, Rani Mukerji, Indrani Haldar and Sabyasachi Chakraborty in the lead roles. It marks the debut of Rani Mukerji.

Film :: Biyer Phool
Song :: Mon Aamar Ek Natun
Singer :: Kumar Sanu, Bijayeta
Music Director :: Jatin-Lalit
